HEADWORD: Unstack
<hw>Un*stack"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>stack</ets>.]</ety> <def>To remove, or take away,
from a stack; to remove, as something constituting a stack.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

